{
  "video_id": "N7wF2AdVy2Q",
  "title": "How frustration can make us more creative | Tim Harford",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15400.0,
      "text": "Late in January 1975,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15400.0,
      "end_time": 19840.0,
      "text": "a 17-year-old German girl called Vera Brandes"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19840.0,
      "end_time": 24240.0,
      "text": "walked out onto the stage of the Cologne Opera House."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24240.0,
      "end_time": 27040.0,
      "text": "The auditorium was empty."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27040.0,
      "end_time": 32200.0,
      "text": "It was lit only by the dim, green glow of the emergency exit sign."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32200.000000000004,
      "end_time": 36160.0,
      "text": "This was the most exciting day of Vera&#39;s life."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36160.0,
      "end_time": 39200.0,
      "text": "She was the youngest concert promoter in Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39200.0,
      "end_time": 41640.0,
      "text": "and she had persuaded the Cologne Opera House"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41640.0,
      "end_time": 45000.0,
      "text": "to host a late-night concert of jazz"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45000.0,
      "end_time": 48800.0,
      "text": "from the American musician, Keith Jarrett."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 51840.0,
      "text": "1,400 people were coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51840.0,
      "end_time": 53440.0,
      "text": "And in just a few hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53440.0,
      "end_time": 55880.0,
      "text": "Jarrett would walk out on the same stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55880.0,
      "end_time": 57240.0,
      "text": "he&#39;d sit down at the piano"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57240.0,
      "end_time": 61080.0,
      "text": "and without rehearsal or sheet music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61080.0,
      "end_time": 64320.0,
      "text": "he would begin to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64319.99999999999,
      "end_time": 65560.0,
      "text": "But right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65560.0,
      "end_time": 69160.0,
      "text": "Vera was introducing Keith to the piano in question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69160.0,
      "end_time": 71120.0,
      "text": "and it wasn&#39;t going well."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71120.0,
      "end_time": 73800.0,
      "text": "Jarrett looked to the instrument a little warily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73800.0,
      "end_time": 75360.0,
      "text": "played a few notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75360.0,
      "end_time": 76599.0,
      "text": "walked around it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76599.0,
      "end_time": 78080.0,
      "text": "played a few more notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78080.0,
      "end_time": 79800.0,
      "text": "muttered something to his producer."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79800.0,
      "end_time": 84280.0,
      "text": "Then the producer came over to Vera and said ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84280.0,
      "end_time": 90000.0,
      "text": "&quot;If you don&#39;t get a new piano, Keith can&#39;t play.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90000.0,
      "end_time": 91480.0,
      "text": "There&#39;d been a mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91480.0,
      "end_time": 93880.0,
      "text": "The opera house had provided the wrong instrument."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93880.0,
      "end_time": 96560.0,
      "text": "This one had this harsh, tinny upper register,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96560.0,
      "end_time": 99640.0,
      "text": "because all the felt had worn away."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99640.0,
      "end_time": 102800.0,
      "text": "The black notes were sticking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102800.0,
      "end_time": 104720.0,
      "text": "the white notes were out of tune,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104720.0,
      "end_time": 106400.0,
      "text": "the pedals didn&#39;t work"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106400.0,
      "end_time": 108600.0,
      "text": "and the piano itself was just too small."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 108600.0,
      "end_time": 110040.0,
      "text": "It wouldn&#39;t create the volume"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110040.0,
      "end_time": 114520.0,
      "text": "that would fill a large space such as the Cologne Opera House."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114520.0,
      "end_time": 118400.0,
      "text": "So Keith Jarrett left."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118400.0,
      "end_time": 121040.0,
      "text": "He went and sat outside in his car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121040.0,
      "end_time": 123000.0,
      "text": "leaving Vera Brandes"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123000.0,
      "end_time": 127680.0,
      "text": "to get on the phone to try to find a replacement piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127680.0,
      "end_time": 129320.0,
      "text": "Now she got a piano tuner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129320.0,
      "end_time": 132160.0,
      "text": "but she couldn&#39;t get a new piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132160.0,
      "end_time": 134880.0,
      "text": "And so she went outside"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134880.0,
      "end_time": 137520.0,
      "text": "and she stood there in the rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137520.0,
      "end_time": 140000.0,
      "text": "talking to Keith Jarrett,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140000.0,
      "end_time": 144160.0,
      "text": "begging him not to cancel the concert."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 145600.0,
      "text": "And he looked out of his car"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145600.0,
      "end_time": 150280.0,
      "text": "at this bedraggled, rain-drenched German teenager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150280.0,
      "end_time": 152080.0,
      "text": "took pity on her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152080.0,
      "end_time": 153960.0,
      "text": "and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153960.0,
      "end_time": 159120.0,
      "text": "&quot;Never forget ... only for you.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 159120.0,
      "end_time": 160920.0,
      "text": "And so a few hours later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160920.0,
      "end_time": 165400.0,
      "text": "Jarrett did indeed step out onto the stage of the opera house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165400.0,
      "end_time": 169600.0,
      "text": "he sat down at the unplayable piano"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169600.0,
      "end_time": 171320.0,
      "text": "and began."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171320.0,
      "end_time": 184720.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 184720.0,
      "end_time": 190080.0,
      "text": "Within moments it became clear that something magical was happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190080.0,
      "end_time": 192680.0,
      "text": "Jarrett was avoiding those upper registers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192680.0,
      "end_time": 195320.0,
      "text": "he was sticking to the middle tones of the keyboard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195320.0,
      "end_time": 199960.0,
      "text": "which gave the piece a soothing, ambient quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199960.0,
      "end_time": 202520.0,
      "text": "But also, because the piano was so quiet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202520.0,
      "end_time": 206960.0,
      "text": "he had to set up these rumbling, repetitive riffs in the bass."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206960.0,
      "end_time": 212240.0,
      "text": "And he stood up twisting, pounding down on the keys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 212240.0,
      "end_time": 217880.0,
      "text": "desperately trying to create enough volume to reach the people in the back row."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217880.0,
      "end_time": 219920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an electrifying performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 219920.0,
      "end_time": 222880.0,
      "text": "It somehow has this peaceful quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 222880.0,
      "end_time": 224960.0,
      "text": "and at the same time it&#39;s full of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 224960.0,
      "end_time": 227200.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s dynamic."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 227200.0,
      "end_time": 229560.0,
      "text": "And the audience loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229560.0,
      "end_time": 231240.0,
      "text": "Audiences continue to love it"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231240.0,
      "end_time": 234360.0,
      "text": "because the recording of the KÃ¶ln Concert"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234360.0,
      "end_time": 236880.0,
      "text": "is the best-selling piano album in history"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236880.0,
      "end_time": 242560.0,
      "text": "and the best-selling solo jazz album in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242560.0,
      "end_time": 246280.0,
      "text": "Keith Jarrett had been handed a mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246280.0,
      "end_time": 252520.0,
      "text": "He had embraced that mess, and it soared."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 252520.0,
      "end_time": 257360.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s think for a moment about Jarrett&#39;s initial instinct."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 257360.0,
      "end_time": 258960.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t want to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 258959.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260199.99999999997,
      "text": "Of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260200.0,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "I think any of us, in any remotely similar situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 265760.0,
      "text": "would feel the same way, we&#39;d have the same instinct."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 265760.0,
      "end_time": 269079.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want to be asked to do good work with bad tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269079.0,
      "end_time": 274160.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want to have to overcome unnecessary hurdles."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274160.0,
      "end_time": 277120.0,
      "text": "But Jarrett&#39;s instinct was wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 277120.0,
      "end_time": 279840.0,
      "text": "and thank goodness he changed his mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279840.0,
      "end_time": 284800.0,
      "text": "And I think our instinct is also wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 284800.0,
      "end_time": 288240.0,
      "text": "I think we need to gain a bit more appreciation"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288240.0,
      "end_time": 295560.0,
      "text": "for the unexpected advantages of having to cope with a little mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295560.0,
      "end_time": 297720.0,
      "text": "So let me give you some examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297720.0,
      "end_time": 300200.0,
      "text": "from cognitive psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 300200.0,
      "end_time": 301640.0,
      "text": "from complexity science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301640.0,
      "end_time": 303120.0,
      "text": "from social psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 303120.0,
      "end_time": 305680.0,
      "text": "and of course, rock &#39;n&#39; roll."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 305680.0,
      "end_time": 307760.0,
      "text": "So cognitive psychology first."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 307760.0,
      "end_time": 309600.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve actually known for a while"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 309600.0,
      "end_time": 311960.0,
      "text": "that certain kinds of difficulty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311960.0,
      "end_time": 313560.0,
      "text": "certain kinds of obstacle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313560.0,
      "end_time": 315346.0,
      "text": "can actually improve our performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315346.0,
      "end_time": 317080.0,
      "text": "For example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 317080.0,
      "end_time": 318840.0,
      "text": "the psychologist Daniel Oppenheimer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318840.0,
      "end_time": 320080.0,
      "text": "a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 320080.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "teamed up with high school teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 322160.0,
      "end_time": 324920.0,
      "text": "And he asked them to reformat the handouts"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 324920.0,
      "end_time": 328200.0,
      "text": "that they were giving to some of their classes."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328200.0,
      "end_time": 331558.0,
      "text": "So the regular handout would be formatted in something straightforward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 331558.0,
      "end_time": 334840.0,
      "text": "such as Helvetica or Times New Roman."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 334840.0,
      "end_time": 337880.0,
      "text": "But half these classes were getting handouts that were formatted"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 337880.0,
      "end_time": 341600.0,
      "text": "in something sort of intense, like Haettenschweiler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341600.0,
      "end_time": 345640.0,
      "text": "or something with a zesty bounce, like Comic Sans italicized."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345640.0,
      "end_time": 347480.0,
      "text": "Now, these are really ugly fonts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 347480.0,
      "end_time": 349680.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re difficult fonts to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 349680.0,
      "end_time": 351800.0,
      "text": "But at the end of the semester,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 351800.0,
      "end_time": 354440.0,
      "text": "students were given exams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354440.0,
      "end_time": 358120.0,
      "text": "and the students who&#39;d been asked to read the more difficult fonts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 358120.0,
      "end_time": 360200.0,
      "text": "had actually done better on their exams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 360200.0,
      "end_time": 361760.0,
      "text": "in a variety of subjects."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 361760.0,
      "end_time": 363800.0,
      "text": "And the reason is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 363800.0,
      "end_time": 366360.0,
      "text": "the difficult font had slowed them down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 366360.0,
      "end_time": 368440.0,
      "text": "forced them to work a bit harder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 368440.0,
      "end_time": 371040.0,
      "text": "to think a bit more about what they were reading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 371040.0,
      "end_time": 373360.0,
      "text": "to interpret it ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 373360.0,
      "end_time": 376320.0,
      "text": "and so they learned more."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 376320.0,
      "end_time": 378760.0,
      "text": "Another example."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 378760.0,
      "end_time": 383880.0,
      "text": "The psychologist Shelley Carson has been testing Harvard undergraduates"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 383880.0,
      "end_time": 386880.0,
      "text": "for the quality of their attentional filters."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 386880.0,
      "end_time": 388280.0,
      "text": "What do I mean by that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 388280.0,
      "end_time": 390520.0,
      "text": "What I mean is, imagine you&#39;re in a restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 390520.0,
      "end_time": 392280.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re having a conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 392280.0,
      "end_time": 395440.0,
      "text": "there are all kinds of other conversations going on in the restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 395440.0,
      "end_time": 396800.0,
      "text": "you want to filter them out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 396800.0,
      "end_time": 398960.0,
      "text": "you want to focus on what&#39;s important to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 398960.0,
      "end_time": 400200.0,
      "text": "Can you do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 400200.0,
      "end_time": 403200.0,
      "text": "If you can, you have good, strong attentional filters."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 403200.0,
      "end_time": 405280.0,
      "text": "But some people really struggle with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 405280.0,
      "end_time": 409040.0,
      "text": "Some of Carson&#39;s undergraduate subjects struggled with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 409040.0,
      "end_time": 412000.0,
      "text": "They had weak filters, they had porous filters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 412000.0,
      "end_time": 415400.0,
      "text": "let a lot of external information in."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 415400.0,
      "end_time": 418560.0,
      "text": "And so what that meant is they were constantly being interrupted"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 418560.0,
      "end_time": 421160.0,
      "text": "by the sights and the sounds of the world around them."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 421160.0,
      "end_time": 424240.0,
      "text": "If there was a television on while they were doing their essays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 424240.0,
      "end_time": 425680.0,
      "text": "they couldn&#39;t screen it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 425680.0,
      "end_time": 429480.0,
      "text": "Now, you would think that that was a disadvantage ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 429480.0,
      "end_time": 430720.0,
      "text": "but no."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 430720.0,
      "end_time": 434720.0,
      "text": "When Carson looked at what these students had achieved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 434720.0,
      "end_time": 436520.0,
      "text": "the ones with the weak filters"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 436520.0,
      "end_time": 438960.0,
      "text": "were vastly more likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 438960.0,
      "end_time": 441760.0,
      "text": "to have some real creative milestone in their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 441760.0,
      "end_time": 444120.0,
      "text": "to have published their first novel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 444120.0,
      "end_time": 447200.0,
      "text": "to have released their first album."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 447200.0,
      "end_time": 450920.0,
      "text": "These distractions were actually grists to their creative mill."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 450920.0,
      "end_time": 456200.0,
      "text": "They were able to think outside the box because their box was full of holes."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 456200.0,
      "end_time": 457960.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about complexity science."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 457960.0,
      "end_time": 459842.0,
      "text": "So how do you solve a really complex --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459842.0,
      "end_time": 461880.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s full of complicated problems --"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 461880.0,
      "end_time": 464080.0,
      "text": "how do you solve a really complicated problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 464080.0,
      "end_time": 466240.0,
      "text": "For example, you try to make a jet engine."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 466240.0,
      "end_time": 468480.0,
      "text": "There are lots and lots of different variables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 468480.0,
      "end_time": 470457.0,
      "text": "the operating temperature, the materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 470457.0,
      "end_time": 472920.0,
      "text": "all the different dimensions, the shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 472920.0,
      "end_time": 475480.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t solve that kind of problem all in one go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 475480.0,
      "end_time": 476720.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s too hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 476720.0,
      "end_time": 477960.0,
      "text": "So what do you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 477960.0,
      "end_time": 482920.0,
      "text": "Well, one thing you can do is try to solve it step-by-step."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 482920.0,
      "end_time": 484640.0,
      "text": "So you have some kind of prototype"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 484640.0,
      "end_time": 488080.0,
      "text": "and you tweak it, you test it, you improve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 488080.0,
      "end_time": 492040.0,
      "text": "You tweak it, you test it, you improve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 492040.0,
      "end_time": 497560.0,
      "text": "Now, this idea of marginal gains will eventually get you a good jet engine."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 497560.0,
      "end_time": 500880.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s been quite widely implemented in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 500880.0,
      "end_time": 504400.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;ll hear about it, for example, in high performance cycling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 504400.0,
      "end_time": 507720.0,
      "text": "web designers will talk about trying to optimize their web pages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 507720.0,
      "end_time": 510040.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re looking for these step-by-step gains."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 510040.0,
      "end_time": 514440.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a good way to solve a complicated problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 514440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518600.00000000006,
      "text": "But you know what would make it a better way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 518600.0,
      "end_time": 521320.0,
      "text": "A dash of mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 521320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523360.00000000006,
      "text": "You add randomness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 523360.0,
      "end_time": 524760.0,
      "text": "early on in the process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 524760.0,
      "end_time": 526280.0,
      "text": "you make crazy moves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 526280.0,
      "end_time": 529679.0,
      "text": "you try stupid things that shouldn&#39;t work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 529679.0,
      "end_time": 532720.0,
      "text": "and that will tend to make the problem-solving work better."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 532720.0,
      "end_time": 534280.0,
      "text": "And the reason for that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 534280.0,
      "end_time": 536360.0,
      "text": "the trouble with the step-by-step process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 536360.0,
      "end_time": 537600.0,
      "text": "the marginal gains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 537600.0,
      "end_time": 541160.0,
      "text": "is they can walk you gradually down a dead end."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 541160.0,
      "end_time": 545400.0,
      "text": "And if you start with the randomness, that becomes less likely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 545400.0,
      "end_time": 550440.0,
      "text": "and your problem-solving becomes more robust."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 550440.0,
      "end_time": 552720.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about social psychology."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 552720.0,
      "end_time": 555840.0,
      "text": "So the psychologist Katherine Phillips, with some colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 555840.0,
      "end_time": 559920.0,
      "text": "recently gave murder mystery problems to some students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 559920.0,
      "end_time": 562800.0,
      "text": "and these students were collected in groups of four"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 562800.0,
      "end_time": 566160.0,
      "text": "and they were given dossiers with information about a crime --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 566160.0,
      "end_time": 571000.0,
      "text": "alibis and evidence, witness statements and three suspects."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 571000.0,
      "end_time": 575200.0,
      "text": "And the groups of four students were asked to figure out who did it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 575200.0,
      "end_time": 577280.0,
      "text": "who committed the crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 577280.0,
      "end_time": 580760.0,
      "text": "And there were two treatments in this experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 580760.0,
      "end_time": 584000.0,
      "text": "In some cases these were four friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 584000.0,
      "end_time": 586160.0,
      "text": "they all knew each other well."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 586160.0,
      "end_time": 587960.0,
      "text": "In other cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587960.0,
      "end_time": 591040.0,
      "text": "three friends and a stranger."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 591040.0,
      "end_time": 593120.0,
      "text": "And you can see where I&#39;m going with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 593120.0,
      "end_time": 594400.0,
      "text": "Obviously I&#39;m going to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 594400.0,
      "end_time": 597840.0,
      "text": "that the groups with the stranger solved the problem more effectively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 597840.0,
      "end_time": 599800.0,
      "text": "which is true, they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 599800.0,
      "end_time": 603320.0,
      "text": "Actually, they solved the problem quite a lot more effectively."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 603320.0,
      "end_time": 607120.0,
      "text": "So the groups of four friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 607120.0,
      "end_time": 610120.0,
      "text": "they only had a 50-50 chance of getting the answer right."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 610120.0,
      "end_time": 611840.0,
      "text": "Which is actually not that great --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 611840.0,
      "end_time": 614800.0,
      "text": "in multiple choice, for three answers? 50-50&#39;s not good."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 614800.0,
      "end_time": 616000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 616000.0,
      "end_time": 617720.0,
      "text": "The three friends and the stranger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 617720.0,
      "end_time": 620560.0,
      "text": "even though the stranger didn&#39;t have any extra information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 620560.0,
      "end_time": 622120.0,
      "text": "even though it was just a case"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 622120.0,
      "end_time": 628440.0,
      "text": "of how that changed the conversation to accommodate that awkwardness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 628440.0,
      "end_time": 630160.0,
      "text": "the three friends and the stranger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 630160.0,
      "end_time": 632850.0,
      "text": "they had a 75 percent chance of finding the right answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 632850.0,
      "end_time": 634600.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s quite a big leap in performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 634600.0,
      "end_time": 636960.0,
      "text": "But I think what&#39;s really interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 636960.0,
      "end_time": 640223.0,
      "text": "is not just that the three friends and the stranger did a better job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 640223.0,
      "end_time": 642400.0,
      "text": "but how they felt about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 642400.0,
      "end_time": 647360.0,
      "text": "So when Katherine Phillips interviewed the groups of four friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 647360.0,
      "end_time": 649240.0,
      "text": "they had a nice time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 649240.0,
      "end_time": 652720.0,
      "text": "they also thought they&#39;d done a good job."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 652720.0,
      "end_time": 654800.0,
      "text": "They were complacent."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 654800.0,
      "end_time": 657320.0,
      "text": "When she spoke to the three friends and the stranger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 657320.0,
      "end_time": 658840.0,
      "text": "they had not had a nice time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 658840.0,
      "end_time": 662480.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s actually rather difficult, it&#39;s rather awkward ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 662480.0,
      "end_time": 666200.0,
      "text": "and they were full of doubt."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 666200.0,
      "end_time": 670080.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t think they&#39;d done a good job even though they had."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 670080.0,
      "end_time": 671840.0,
      "text": "And I think that really exemplifies"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 671840.0,
      "end_time": 674680.0,
      "text": "the challenge that we&#39;re dealing with here."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 674680.0,
      "end_time": 676520.0,
      "text": "Because, yeah --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 676520.0,
      "end_time": 678400.0,
      "text": "the ugly font,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 678400.0,
      "end_time": 680200.0,
      "text": "the awkward stranger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 680200.0,
      "end_time": 682280.0,
      "text": "the random move ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 682280.0,
      "end_time": 685680.0,
      "text": "these disruptions help us solve problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 685680.0,
      "end_time": 688040.0,
      "text": "they help us become more creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 688040.0,
      "end_time": 690120.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t feel that they&#39;re helping us."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 690120.0,
      "end_time": 693040.0,
      "text": "We feel that they&#39;re getting in the way ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 693040.0,
      "end_time": 696000.0,
      "text": "and so we resist."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 696000.0,
      "end_time": 699360.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s why the last example is really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 699360.0,
      "end_time": 701600.0,
      "text": "So I want to talk about somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 701600.0,
      "end_time": 706560.0,
      "text": "from the background of the world of rock &#39;n&#39; roll."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 706560.0,
      "end_time": 709480.0,
      "text": "And you may know him, he&#39;s actually a TED-ster."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 709480.0,
      "end_time": 710880.0,
      "text": "His name is Brian Eno."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 710880.0,
      "end_time": 713720.0,
      "text": "He is an ambient composer -- rather brilliant."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 713720.0,
      "end_time": 717160.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s also a kind of catalyst"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 717160.0,
      "end_time": 721200.0,
      "text": "behind some of the great rock &#39;n&#39; roll albums of the last 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 721200.0,
      "end_time": 724840.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s worked with David Bowie on &quot;Heroes,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 724840.0,
      "end_time": 728000.0,
      "text": "he worked with U2 on &quot;Achtung Baby&quot; and &quot;The Joshua Tree,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 728000.0,
      "end_time": 729560.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s worked with DEVO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 729560.0,
      "end_time": 732160.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s worked with Coldplay, he&#39;s worked with everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 732160.0,
      "end_time": 737720.0,
      "text": "And what does he do to make these great rock bands better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 737720.0,
      "end_time": 739840.0,
      "text": "Well, he makes a mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 739840.0,
      "end_time": 741680.0,
      "text": "He disrupts their creative processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 741680.0,
      "end_time": 743800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s his role to be the awkward stranger."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 743800.0,
      "end_time": 745240.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s his role to tell them"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 745240.0,
      "end_time": 748440.0,
      "text": "that they have to play the unplayable piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 748440.0,
      "end_time": 751120.0,
      "text": "And one of the ways in which he creates this disruption"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 751120.0,
      "end_time": 754680.0,
      "text": "is through this remarkable deck of cards --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 754680.0,
      "end_time": 758560.0,
      "text": "I have my signed copy here -- thank you, Brian."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 758560.0,
      "end_time": 760440.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re called The Oblique Strategies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 760440.0,
      "end_time": 762800.0,
      "text": "he developed them with a friend of his."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 762800.0,
      "end_time": 766880.0,
      "text": "And when they&#39;re stuck in the studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 766880.0,
      "end_time": 769200.0,
      "text": "Brian Eno will reach for one of the cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 769200.0,
      "end_time": 770680.0,
      "text": "He&#39;ll draw one at random,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 770680.0,
      "end_time": 774960.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;ll make the band follow the instructions on the card."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 774960.0,
      "end_time": 777040.0,
      "text": "So this one ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 777040.0,
      "end_time": 778360.0,
      "text": "&quot;Change instrument roles.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 778360.0,
      "end_time": 781099.0,
      "text": "Yeah, everyone swap instruments -- Drummer on the piano --"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 781099.0,
      "end_time": 783120.0,
      "text": "Brilliant, brilliant idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 783120.0,
      "end_time": 788360.0,
      "text": "&quot;Look closely at the most embarrassing details. Amplify them.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 788360.0,
      "end_time": 794960.0,
      "text": "&quot;Make a sudden, destructive, unpredictable action. Incorporate.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 794960.0,
      "end_time": 797080.0,
      "text": "These cards are disruptive."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 797080.0,
      "end_time": 801880.0,
      "text": "Now, they&#39;ve proved their worth in album after album."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 801880.0,
      "end_time": 804200.0,
      "text": "The musicians hate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 804200.0,
      "end_time": 805720.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 805720.0,
      "end_time": 809160.0,
      "text": "So Phil Collins was playing drums on an early Brian Eno album."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 809160.0,
      "end_time": 814400.0,
      "text": "He got so frustrated he started throwing beer cans across the studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 814400.0,
      "end_time": 816800.0,
      "text": "Carlos Alomar, great rock guitarist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 816800.0,
      "end_time": 820600.0,
      "text": "working with Eno on David Bowie&#39;s &quot;Lodger&quot; album,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 820600.0,
      "end_time": 823200.0,
      "text": "and at one point he turns to Brian and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 823200.0,
      "end_time": 829360.0,
      "text": "&quot;Brian, this experiment is stupid.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 829360.0,
      "end_time": 833120.0,
      "text": "But the thing is it was a pretty good album,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 833120.0,
      "end_time": 835040.0,
      "text": "but also,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 835040.0,
      "end_time": 839880.0,
      "text": "Carlos Alomar, 35 years later, now uses The Oblique Strategies."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 839880.0,
      "end_time": 842640.0,
      "text": "And he tells his students to use The Oblique Strategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 842640.0,
      "end_time": 845240.0,
      "text": "because he&#39;s realized something."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 845240.0,
      "end_time": 852000.0,
      "text": "Just because you don&#39;t like it doesn&#39;t mean it isn&#39;t helping you."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 852000.0,
      "end_time": 854786.0,
      "text": "The strategies actually weren&#39;t a deck of cards originally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 854786.0,
      "end_time": 856000.0,
      "text": "they were just a list --"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 856000.0,
      "end_time": 857840.0,
      "text": "list on the recording studio wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 857840.0,
      "end_time": 863280.0,
      "text": "A checklist of things you might try if you got stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 863280.0,
      "end_time": 866160.0,
      "text": "The list didn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 866160.0,
      "end_time": 869400.0,
      "text": "Know why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 869400.0,
      "end_time": 871680.0,
      "text": "Not messy enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 871680.0,
      "end_time": 873720.0,
      "text": "Your eye would go down the list"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 873720.0,
      "end_time": 877800.0,
      "text": "and it would settle on whatever was the least disruptive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 877800.0,
      "end_time": 880480.0,
      "text": "the least troublesome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 880480.0,
      "end_time": 886160.0,
      "text": "which of course misses the point entirely."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 886160.0,
      "end_time": 888560.0,
      "text": "And what Brian Eno came to realize was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 888560.0,
      "end_time": 893080.0,
      "text": "yes, we need to run the stupid experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 893080.0,
      "end_time": 895160.0,
      "text": "we need to deal with the awkward strangers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 895160.0,
      "end_time": 897320.0,
      "text": "we need to try to read the ugly fonts."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 897320.0,
      "end_time": 898600.0,
      "text": "These things help us."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 898600.0,
      "end_time": 900000.0,
      "text": "They help us solve problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 900000.0,
      "end_time": 901920.0,
      "text": "they help us be more creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 901920.0,
      "end_time": 904320.0,
      "text": "But also ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 904320.0,
      "end_time": 908200.0,
      "text": "we really need some persuasion if we&#39;re going to accept this."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 908200.0,
      "end_time": 910400.0,
      "text": "So however we do it ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 910400.0,
      "end_time": 912480.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s sheer willpower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 912480.0,
      "end_time": 915560.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s the flip of a card"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 915560.0,
      "end_time": 919680.0,
      "text": "or whether it&#39;s a guilt trip from a German teenager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 919680.0,
      "end_time": 921840.0,
      "text": "all of us, from time to time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 921840.0,
      "end_time": 927640.0,
      "text": "need to sit down and try and play the unplayable piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 927640.0,
      "end_time": 928880.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 928880.0,
      "end_time": 938880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}